g.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Ddz4wBt4bvcE&d=LRk9npnliL4HefRMP%2BWOkG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=d71e5177\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dz4wBt4bvcE</a><br />\n《臭隨著你》   原曲 ： 伴隨著你--粵語版<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">其實你是有精味</span><br />\n在天際的深處<br />\n有座美麗雷泊特<br />\n隱隱的飄浮雲中央<br />\n<br />\n仍未揭露它真相<br />\n又未找到它方向<br />\n願望能有日向天空飛去<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">碌尻臭過屎尿屁</span><br />\n<br />\n探訪天際的家鄉<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">叢林裡面有賓周</span><br />\n尋覓快樂溫馨的愛巢<br />\n心中的理想<br />\n<br />\n在天空中有座城<br />\n有小野花飄香<br />\n在天空中有座城<br />\n鳥聲似歌柔揚<br />\n<br />\n凝視我望向天上<br />\n在心裡輕輕唱<br />\n朦朧我像聽到了<br />\n家鄉的鳥兒在和唱<br />\n<br />\n誰願意伴我一路盡力找到它方向<br />\n願望能有日向天空飛去<br />\n找到我理想路向<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有無接力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗唔撚到呀"},{"pid":"8c08d9080e8a2f0a051ff811e19fc8e53b842ce1","tid":115920,"uid":28472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T14:34:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>打得j多其實係咪會特別有陣味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定係洗得唔乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前幫男朋友含個時，一除褲已經好撚臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要幫佢含，含含下仲有甩鳩毛係我口入面，勁唔舒服好撚想嘔，真係好撚大陣味</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n絲打一定好愛條仔，咁都幫佢含<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我條女肯咁就好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n下<br />\n我女朋友一路含一路話有味 但又含到雪雪聲 又話好鐘意喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都理解唔到佢諗乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06466378a5738425e1e46b0e85c4268bd49b2476","tid":115920,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T15:22:13.000Z","msg":"試下噴下香水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e7f6502b8a2854169f2e6d0023bb2367eb99209","tid":115920,"uid":37415,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"repl